						<summary>

						<p>Damaged at the end. Begins with the eulogy of the King. It records the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> in the village Vaḍakuṟuchchi in Āriyā-nāḍu to the temple of Piṇakkaṟukku Nāyanār by the king. Koḍumalūruḍaiyāṉ figuars as signatory.</p>						

